OL,3,CBristol's Sikh community gather for
OL,4,CVaisakhi
OL,6,FPeople across Bristol are celebrating
OL,7,FVaisakhi - the festival which
OL,8,Fcelebrates the founding of the Sikh
OL,9,Fcommunity, the Khalsa, in 1699.
OL,11,FThe history of Vaisakhi
OL,13,FIn 1699, Sikhs gathered together to
OL,14,Fcelebrate the local harvest festival
OL,15,Fof Vaisakhi.
OL,17,FThe 10th guru, Guru Gobind Singh,
OL,18,Fasked anyone who was prepared to give
OL,19,Ftheir life for their religion to step
OL,20,Fforward.
