OL,3,CBristol's Sikh community gather for
OL,4,CVaisakhi
OL,6,FA young man stepped forward and went
OL,7,Finto a tent with Guru Gobind Singh.
OL,9,FGuru Gobind Singh came out of the tent
OL,10,Falone with his sword covered in blood
OL,11,Fand asked for another volunteer. This
OL,12,Fhappened another four times.
OL,14,FEveryone was very worried that five
OL,15,Fmen had died but they all came out of
OL,16,Fthe tent wearing turbans. The men
OL,17,Fbecame known as the Panj Piare or
OL,18,F'Beloved Five'.
