OL,3,CBristol's Sikh community gather for
OL,4,CVaisakhi
OL,6,FGuru Gobind Singh baptised all the men
OL,7,Finto the Khalsa. They became the first
OL,8,Fmembers of the Khalsa.
OL,10,FThe word "Khalsa" translates to "pure"
OL,11,For "the pure". Khalsa members are
OL,12,Fexpected to uphold the highest moral
OL,13,Fand ethical standards, representing a
OL,14,Fdisciplined group dedicated to God and
OL,15,Fhumanity.
OL,17,FCelebrations for Vaisakhi
