OL,3,CBristol's Sikh community gather for
OL,4,CVaisakhi
OL,6,FSikhs go to the Gurdwara in the
OL,7,Fmorning for a service. A prayer is
OL,8,Fread continuously for 48 hours,
OL,9,Fstarting at 11am on Friday 18 April.
OL,11,FEvery two hours the reader changes,
OL,12,Fand people of all ages come by all day
OL,13,Fto pray.
OL,15,FThere's also a procession through the
OL,16,Fstreets called Nagar Kirtan which will
OL,17,Ftake place on Saturday 19 April.
OL,19,FIn the evenings, Sikhs have a special
OL,20,Fmeal with family and friends.
