OL,3,CBristol's Sikh community gather for
OL,4,CVaisakhi
OL,6,FNirmal Kaur Bal is the secretary of
OL,7,Fthe Siri Guru Singh Sabha Gurdwara in
OL,8,FBristol.
OL,10,FShe said: "Everybody is so full of
OL,11,Fenergy. It's a really nice atmosphere
OL,12,Fand the children - they love it.
OL,14,F"We want them to enjoy it, to have a
OL,15,Fnice experience. So when they grow up
OL,16,Fthey have some sweet memories and they
OL,17,Fhave learned something good."
